<quantity box="[196,254,321,348]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="25" pageNumber="84" unit="cm" value="2.0">2 cm</quantity>
above ground; corm with a crescentshaped basal ridge. Leaves 3-5, lower 2 basal, narrowly 4-grooved, 
<quantity box="[380,468,382,409]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="25" pageNumber="84" unit="mm" value="0.5">0.5 mm</quantity>
diam.; outer bracts with narrow membranous margins, inner bracts with wide brown-speckled membranous margins. Flowers orange-yellow with dark marks in the cup, sweetly scented, tepals elliptic, 
<quantity box="[563,683,505,532]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.6" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.2" pageId="25" pageNumber="84" unit="mm" value="16.0" valueMax="20.0" valueMin="12.0">12-20 mm</quantity>
